{"tid":1044150,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[秒經]京都大阪六日五夜行程，求推介餐廳","createTime":"2019-03-02T16:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T16:11:12.000Z","uid":33851,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"12e6de7ca52ffd7b89efdc30e0e9739f7abcf04e","tid":1044150,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:51:08.000Z","msg":"10年無坐過飛機兼成世仔第一次自由行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  帶埋兩老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 凌晨機到關西機場&gt;伏見稻荷&gt;宇治&gt;京都塔<br />\n<br />\nDay2: 嵐山&gt;清水寺&gt;祇園&gt;錦市場<br />\n<br />\nDay3: 北野天滿宮&gt;哲學之道&gt;大文字山&gt;大阪酒店<br />\n<br />\nDay4: 奈良&gt;梅田，道頓堀<br />\n<br />\nDay5: 黑門市場&gt;大阪城&gt;即食麵博物館&gt;天王寺<br />\n<br />\nDay6: 專門店/ Mitsui Outlet Park 去睇戶外用品/ 波鞋/ 藥房/手信 乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n想問下大阪仲有無地方影相好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但又唔想去太多廟宇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋拉麵，炸串，烤肉以外 有無多啲蔬菜既推介清下腸胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n京都夜晚應該近乎死城 無野好行? <br />\n大阪夜晚除左梅田難波仲有無野好行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋keep住搭JR會唔會比私鐵/巴士易上手  啲站會唔會無咁密/兜路，寧願行多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c973261e63fa96f981cc9a5ddc489b48887b0628","tid":1044150,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T16:51:53.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c252286feffc84b7c719d5666adcc235edaff358","tid":1044150,"uid":86948,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:02:24.000Z","msg":"唔自己做資料搜集下下問的話就食金龍啦"},{"pid":"12bff421af66f8c71ba9c8577a02c526b5514e45","tid":1044150,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"你帶住兩老都想行路多小小？"},{"pid":"cee205881f0f2fc7f8e4d2aee7f6d1bb4a7f4a82","tid":1044150,"uid":116487,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:07:11.000Z","msg":"吹奏下蛋包飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/010648_6b8c1603a9149ad5ad796599ccf1edca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F010648_6b8c1603a9149ad5ad796599ccf1edca.png&h=39bb280b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺京都嘅，上網book定位先，好快full<br />\n<a href=\"http://kichi2.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkichi2.net&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEIVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=4fc846ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">kichi2.net</a>"},{"pid":"90a8a969202112a34f3520c004838edbafc35ceb","tid":1044150,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c252286feffc84b7c719d5666adcc235edaff358","tid":1044150,"uid":86948,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:02:24.000Z","msg":"唔自己做資料搜集下下問的話就食金龍啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"主要都係想吹下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋問意見睇下會唔會好易行唔哂或者太快行哂無嘢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食就都有睇出面個大阪食嘢post 主要都係就去嘅景點附近啦  都預等位耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa806b7a767d970efb28ecbd8f5e625c1dce5dc","tid":1044150,"uid":201374,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"帶住兩老搭紅眼機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 凌晨機到關西機場&gt;伏見稻荷&gt;宇治&gt;京都塔<br />\n而且落機完全唔打算休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay2: 嵐山&gt;清水寺&gt;祇園&gt;錦市場<br />\nDay3: 北野天滿宮&gt;哲學之道&gt;大文字山&gt;大阪酒店<br />\nplan行程唔睇地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如你睇吓其他ching嘅遊記或者行程plan先啦<br />\n明知係秒經都唔睇完先問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e758218f298ebb4dad65b6e0303b59ab7b000e1","tid":1044150,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"12bff421af66f8c71ba9c8577a02c526b5514e45","tid":1044150,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"你帶住兩老都想行路多小小？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:10:13.000Z","msg":"之前去澳門 啲巴士慢到得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n坐到急屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正天氣唔熱  行路半個鐘內都ok啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bd29230e7879e746a9b1a45be71b80bbc58cbb","tid":1044150,"uid":180234,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:11:01.000Z","msg":"去大阪一定要食金龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ba87fc208821931db6c12ae9c17871b6271b63","tid":1044150,"uid":86762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T17:57:04.000Z","msg":"大阪城講咗好多次<br />\n對日本歷史冇興趣唔洗去"},{"pid":"3b6dfec29ef3b8ec89a1c6578bbc4ee4426a92eb","tid":1044150,"uid":17359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:10:16.000Z","msg":"Day2: 嵐山&gt;清水寺&gt;祇園&gt;錦市場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先 清水寺而家裝修緊 未到2020年既3月都睇唔到全相<br />\n<br />\n其次 你諗住幾點去錦市場？如果你晏少少去嵐山既話返到黎錦市場已經收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不如掉轉 朝早去左錦市場先，再去祇園<br />\n之後再搭車去嵐山 咁會唔會好d?<br />\n清水寺就算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4337dc5172b02f77a11ad22b31d67d5e7627a62","tid":1044150,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:13:09.000Z","msg":"同埋day1凌晨幾點到關西機場？<br />\nHaruka頭班車好似5點幾"},{"pid":"c755139f2731b1591aa212d8ca71589af3a62ca8","tid":1044150,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T22:21:02.000Z","msg":"我係老唔好再揾餐廳，周街是但入去都好好食，你再加餐廳只會行得仲多，越黎越亂"},{"pid":"744b750798e7cb4a15bfac49f02506422bfd42a7","tid":1044150,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4337dc5172b02f77a11ad22b31d67d5e7627a62","tid":1044150,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:13:09.000Z","msg":"同埋day1凌晨幾點到關西機場？<br />\nHaruka頭班車好似5點幾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:29:50.000Z","msg":"0550到關西  去到食早餐 托運行李乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n同埋學上面巴打話齋要諗諗點樣小休<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17497558d2b8f9081b81e44668a1f5472e8850f6","tid":1044150,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:06:58.000Z","msg":"day 1<br />\n如果一個唔好彩重機訓得唔好的話<br />\n第一日行咁多真係玩死你屋企人<br />\n<br />\nday2 錦市場3點幾4點準備收工自己睇時間<br />\n<br />\nday3 北野天滿宮同哲學之道一個東一個西<br />\n剩係搭車都要大半個鐘仲要行山之後出番大阪<br />\n你似玩野多o的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af56de867dfd451c8b3b463b99547bc9b505c18e","tid":1044150,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"744b750798e7cb4a15bfac49f02506422bfd42a7","tid":1044150,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4337dc5172b02f77a11ad22b31d67d5e7627a62","tid":1044150,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:13:09.000Z","msg":"同埋day1凌晨幾點到關西機場？<br />\nHaruka頭班車好似5點幾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:29:50.000Z","msg":"0550到關西  去到食早餐 托運行李乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n同埋學上面巴打話齋要諗諗點樣小休<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"到酒店之後抖一抖先啦 訓一陣到晏晝再去伏見都未遲 京都塔冇乜特別 係咁咦睇一睇is ok"},{"pid":"afb54cc9382c0590d1e763719fabb5aa407ebc60","tid":1044150,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af56de867dfd451c8b3b463b99547bc9b505c18e","tid":1044150,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"744b750798e7cb4a15bfac49f02506422bfd42a7","tid":1044150,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4337dc5172b02f77a11ad22b31d67d5e7627a62","tid":1044150,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T18:13:09.000Z","msg":"同埋day1凌晨幾點到關西機場？<br />\nHaruka頭班車好似5點幾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:29:50.000Z","msg":"0550到關西  去到食早餐 托運行李乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n同埋學上面巴打話齋要諗諗點樣小休<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"到酒店之後抖一抖先啦 訓一陣到晏晝再去伏見都未遲 京都塔冇乜特別 係咁咦睇一睇is ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"正常酒店邊可能咁早俾你check in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a28c578b7c7e3864cb702e70b623c49aef23ad5","tid":1044150,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afb54cc9382c0590d1e763719fabb5aa407ebc60","tid":1044150,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af56de867dfd451c8b3b463b99547bc9b505c18e","tid":1044150,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"744b750798e7cb4a15bfac49f02506422bfd42a7","tid":1044150,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:29:50.000Z","msg":"0550到關西  去到食早餐 托運行李乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n同埋學上面巴打話齋要諗諗點樣小休<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"到酒店之後抖一抖先啦 訓一陣到晏晝再去伏見都未遲 京都塔冇乜特別 係咁咦睇一睇is ok"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"正常酒店邊可能咁早俾你check in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T14:24:27.0